{"tid":23782,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"學做Web途徑","createTime":"2016-12-05T07:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T08:09:29.000Z","uid":55863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b6d41f6f3d38f0c86221ce9a31458215dfd99bb","tid":23782,"uid":55863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T07:00:29.000Z","msg":"做左幾年Support仔，再做都係冇前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住轉去做Web，自己都有興趣做呢方面<br />\n中學時候都自學過HTML同少少PHP、Javascript、CSS<br />\n<br />\n而家學返Web，應該先學HTML5&gt;CSS3&gt;JS&gt;bootstrap&gt;node.js...？<br />\n定係有其他必要嘅先學？<br />\n上網睇過大陸啲教學影片，有冇啲好嘅教學或者學習途徑？<br />\n<br />\n請大家指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7d036e37750f40edabcb69c9b30a29d9b2de21","tid":23782,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T07:03:20.000Z","msg":"我都係新手<br />\n而家好似係興React + ECMAScript +Babel<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似LIHKG都係用REACT <br />\n不過先有javascript底同PHP都重要既"},{"pid":"be5e4ef3cfd1bc56141050d6b5f227293a70b3f9","tid":23782,"uid":35092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T07:59:26.000Z","msg":"php 就睇下 laravel，好容易上手。"},{"pid":"5475a1d0cba03f1520f5a43e3b9e54aafdcec1b1","tid":23782,"uid":39987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:09:29.000Z","msg":"回頭是岸"}]}